{"word":"G2407 - ἱερατεύω - hierateúō - hee-er-at-yoo'-o - Execute the priest's office","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱερατεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hierateúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hee-er-at-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Execute the priest's office</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆசாரிய ஊழியம் செய்"},{"paragraph":"to be priest, discharge the priest's office, be busied in sacred duties"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolongation from <a href=\"#/G2409 - ἱερεύς - hiereús - hee-er-yooce'/2409\">G2409</a>; to <i>be a priest</i>, that is, <i>perform his functions:</i> - execute the priest&rsquo;s office.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1494/1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405/2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406/2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407/2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409/2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411/2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412/2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413/2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416/2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417/2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418/2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420/2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G749/749\">G749</a>"}]}